            <section class="section-features">
                
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-1-of-4">
                        <div class="feature-box">
                            <i class="feature-box__icon icon-basic-world"></i>
                            <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">Explore the world</h3>
                            <p class="feature-box__text">
                                ‘’Travel makes you realize that no matter how much you know, there’s always more to learn.’’ <strong><br>– John Amatt</strong>                   </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-1-of-4">
                        <div class="feature-box">
                            <i class="feature-box__icon icon-basic-compass"></i>
                            <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">Meet nature</h3>
                            <p class="feature-box__text">
                                “I see my path, but I don’t know where it leads. Not knowing where I’m going is what inspires me to travel it.”<strong><br>-Ralph Waldo Emerson</strong> 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-1-of-4">
                        <div class="feature-box">
                            <i class="feature-box__icon icon-basic-map"></i>
                            <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">Find your way</h3>
                             <p class="feature-box__text">
                                “For my part, I travel not to go anywhere but to go. I travel for travel’s sake. The great affair is to move.” <strong><br>-Robert Louis Stevenson</strong>
