                    </video>
                </div>

                <div class="u-center-text u-margin-bottom-big">
                    <h2 class="heading-secondary">
                        We make people genuinely happy
                    </h2>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="story">
                        <figure class="story__shape">
                            <img src="img/nat-8.jpg" alt="Person on a tour" class="story__img">
                            <figcaption class="story__caption">Lovelyn Singh</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                        <div class="story__text">
                            <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">I had the best week.</h3>
                            <p>
                                The Dream I Was Chasing For Long Many Years To Fly In The Blue Sky Was Just Meant To Be My Only Destination The Paths Which I Had Chose Included Every Hurdle Along With It However I Had Never Given Up On My Dreams Nor Will I Ever Do That 🙃 Without Dreams A Person Its Like A Rudderless Ship Without A Destination There Are No Paths That Really Matters So with a fixed heart intent im on my way to discover the maximum of this earth 🌍 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="story">
                        <figure class="story__shape">
                            <img src="img/nat-9.jpg" alt="Person on a tour" class="story__img">
                            <figcaption class="story__caption">Jeet Singh</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                        <div class="story__text">
                            <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">Corporate life to Nomad Life</h3>
                            <p>
                                When I Had Began My Journey 4 Years Back Nothing Was Left With Me Except The Fact Some Savings Which Was Kept During My Corporate Life 👩‍💻 Those Were Than & Now A Nomad Road Life ✈️ Days Passing By Like Wish Could Stop The Time ⏱ & Say Wow God Damn That’s Simply So Large I’m Living Life & Breathing In The Valleys ⛰Like An independent Bird Flying In The Blue Sky Such Speechlessness Words Are Not Enough To Describe My Insane Travel Stories In Words However I Would Pen It Down With So Much Excitement Within Me Like An Honest Writer Absolutely Than Forever Restoring Memories Like It’s Seems Life Can’t Be Much Real Than This Had Accumulated The Vast Assets In Me Cherishing 😇 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="u-center-text u-margin-top-huge">
                    <a href="#" class="btn-text">Read all stories &rarr;</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="section-book" id= "comehere">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="book">
                        <div class="book__form">
                            <form action="#" class="form">
                                <div class="u-margin-bottom-medium">
                                    <h2 class="heading-secondary">
                                        Contact us!
                                    </h2>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form__group">
                                    <input type="text" class="form__input" placeholder="Full name" id="name" required>
                                    <label for="name" class="form__label">Full name</label>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form__group">
                                    <input type="email" class="form__input" placeholder="Email address" id="email" required>
                                    <label for="email" class="form__label">Email address</label>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form__group u-margin-bottom-medium">
                                    <div class="form__radio-group">
                                        <input type="radio" class="form__radio-input" id="small" name="size">
                                        <label for="small" class="form__radio-label">
                                            <span class="form__radio-button"></span>
                                            Small tour group
                                        </label>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="form__radio-group">
                                        <input type="radio" class="form__radio-input" id="large" name="size">
                                        <label for="large" class="form__radio-label">
                                            <span class="form__radio-button"></span>
                                            Large tour group
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form__group">
                                    <button class="btn btn--green">Contact! &rarr;</button>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
